name: Fed’s Miran: Stablecoins Are ‘Transformational’ for Emerging Markets
description: Brass anatomy kneels, receiving the $3T data-current. The post-organic ritual validates global liquidity, siphoning cyan finance-fluid from the lattice-spires above. The tarnished cube is the sacred ledger, aligning the supplicant’s soft circuitry with the merciless flow of the digital market engine.
